es-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em>《Ascent Of Ashes》</em>是一款即将推出的殖民地模拟游戏，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/rimworld"><em>《RimWorld》</em></a> Combat Extended mod 的创作者打造，将于 11 月进入抢先体验。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/how-endless-dungeon-creates-cosmic-cowboy-vibes-with-singer-lera-lynn-3506474">《无尽地牢》如何与歌手 Lera Lynn 一起创造“宇宙牛仔氛围”</a></strong></li></ul><p>开发商 Vivid Storm Interactive 和发行商 Camlann Games 共同打造的殖民地模拟游戏从<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dwarf-fortress">《矮人要塞》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/jagged-alliance">《铁血联盟》</a> 、《边缘世界》</em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/xcom">《XCOM》</a></em>中汲取灵感，打造出一种艰苦而又令人满意的策略末日体验。</p><p>随着社会在一个已定居的外星球上解体，玩家必须通过其他幸存者的支持来确保安全基地。 “耕种农作物，驯服外星野兽，整合回收的技术，并加固你的家园，抵御敌对入侵者，” <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2209140/Ascent_of_Ashes/?fbclid=IwAR3tpP8EKwb_hJQKdQJw2-OyWqtRv6jVrPi4W5BGlhq7XGC3p9hwDg5Tt8s" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Ascent Of Ashes</em> 》在 Steam 上的描述</a>如此。 </p><figure id="attachment_3507832" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3507832" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3507832" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3507832" class="wp-caption-text"> 《灰烬重生》来源：Camlann Games</figcaption></figure><p>交火中的战斗将是身临其境的，结果多种多样。例如，非致命攻击可能会使一名士兵出局并阻止他们参与其余的战斗。</p><p>此外，敌方人工智能将利用与玩家类似的策略来迎接更大的挑战。开发者解释道：“对抗一群杂乱无章的袭击者与对抗一队训练有素的残余士兵有很大不同。”</p><p>对于那些有兴趣的人来说，游戏也将支持改装，这对团队来说是一个非常重要的补充。</p><p> Vivid Storm Interactive 表示：“我们希望通过<em>《Ascent Of Ashes》</em>回馈这些社区。” “我们正在从头开始构建游戏引擎，以便可以轻松扩展，并且由于我们自己创建模组的丰富经验，我们确切地知道模组制作者需要什么样的支持。” </p><figure id="attachment_3507834" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3507834" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3507834" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ascent-of-Ashes-from-rimworld-developers-arriving-in-nov-3-696x442.jpg