 U2 在 Las Vegas Sphere 驻场演出开幕式上向缺席的鼓手 Larry Mullen Jr 致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-pay-tribute-to-absent-drummer-larry-mullen-jr-at-opening-of-las-vegas-sphere-residency-footage-3507759？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=u2-向缺席的鼓手拉里-马伦-jr-在拉斯维加斯球圈驻场录像开幕式致敬Liberty DunworthMon, 02 Oct 2023 11:29:40 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3507759 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="U2 的 Bono、The Edge、Adam Clayton 和 Bram van den Berg 在 Sphere 的 U2:UV Achtung Baby Live 期间进行表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于肘部、膝盖和颈部受伤，鼓手将不会参加拉斯维加斯的演出</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-pay-tribute-to-absent-drummer-larry-mullen-jr-at-opening-of-las-vegas-sphere-residency-footage-3507759">U2 乐队在 Las Vegas Sphere 驻场演出开幕式上向缺席的鼓手 Larry Mullen Jr 致敬，这首歌曲</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="U2 的 Bono、The Edge、Adam Clayton 和 Bram van den Berg 在 Sphere 的 U2:UV Achtung Baby Live 期间进行表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/U2-Las-Vegas-Sphere@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a>在拉斯维加斯 MSG Sphere 的驻场演出拉开了序幕，他们将其中一首曲目献给鼓手 Larry Mullen Jr，后者因各种受伤而没有参加演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/u2-las-vegas-sphere-setlist-photos-3506848">U2 拉斯维加斯现场演出：在价值 20 亿美元的 Sphere 上呈现令人眼花缭乱的首演之夜</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>上周，爱尔兰摇滚偶像在内华达州的新 MSG Sphere 举办了他们期待已久的驻场演出，并利用开幕表演向缺席的成员致敬。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bono">Bono</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-edge">The Edge</a> 、Adam Clayton 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-discuss-playing-las-vegas-sphere-shows-without-drummer-larry-mullen-jr-3494036">替身鼓手 Bram Van Den Berg</a>在演出期间都向 Mullen Jr 致敬，并将他们 1988 年的歌曲“All I Want Is You”献给他。由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/larry-mullen-jr-says-he-may-not-drum-with-u2-if-the-band-tours-in-2023-3361324">肘部、膝盖和颈部受伤，</a>这位鼓手将不会参加他们在价值 23 亿英镑的场地举行的 25 场驻场演出。</p><p>他此前证实，受伤都是与击鼓有关，并表示他“想花一些时间……让自己痊愈”，而不是坚持参加拉斯维加斯的演出。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-edge-would-be-very-difficult-break-up-u2-3408089">此后有报道称他接受了手术来治疗伤势</a>。</p><p>献给小马伦的表演也是在 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-say-larry-mullen-jr-gave-it-all-on-atomic-city-3506448">乐队公开谈论他</a>在录制新单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-release-anthemic-new-single-atomic-city-3506349">Atomic City</a> 》时在录音室里“掀起一场风暴”后不久进行的，尽管他正在接受手术康复。</p><p> “这对他来说真的很棘手，”波诺在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OfUGtUER1yw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">接受 Apple Music 1 采访</a>时说道。 “他不知道他是否可以打一个小时，或者……他不知道他是否可以打15分钟。他只是渲染了风暴……这对拉里造成了损失。”</p><p>乐队上个月也公开了他的缺席，当时他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-discuss-playing-las-vegas-sphere-shows-without-drummer-larry-mullen-jr-3494036">讨论了没有这位长期成员的表演的感受</a>。</p><p> “整个乐队和我确信观众都会非常悲伤并想念拉里，”贝斯手亚当·克莱顿在接受《<em>每日星</em>报》<em>连线</em>专栏采访时说道。 “他想回来，他希望能够有一个漫长的职业生涯并继续他的鼓手，所以他正在处理这些伤病。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="U2 - 我想要的就是你 - 9-29-2023 - 球体 - 拉斯维加斯" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TxFT_gCOW6k?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该演出于周五（9 月 29 日）举行，是 U2 在可容纳 17,600 人的场馆安排的 25 场演出中的第一场。驻场演出将持续到 12 月，预计乐队将为超过 300,000 人演奏。</p><p>在活动中，乐队完整演奏了 1991 年的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-the-edge-anxious-to-release-new-guitar-driven-album-says-achtung-baby-will-be-centrepiece-of-las-vegas-residency-3409046">《Achtung Baby》</a> ，并演唱了上述新歌《Atomic City》——这是他们自 2021 年发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-explore-power-music-new-track-your-song-saved-my-life-3086726">《Your Song Saved My Life》</a>以来的第一首歌曲。<em>唱2</em>原声带。</p><p>成员们还演奏了一套原声音乐，其中包括他们的《Rattle and Hum》中的歌曲，并以《Elevation》、《Atomic City》、《Vertigo》、《Where the Streets Have No Name》的加演结束了开幕之夜。 《有或没有你》、《美丽的一天》。</p><p>周五演出的其他亮点包括献给<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼爵士</a>的《Desire》、献给已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-buffet">吉米·巴菲特的</a>《Love Rescue Me》以及为成员的家人、朋友和同事表演的《With Or Without You》。</p><p>成员们还通过表演《<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-holiday">哈莱姆天使》向比莉·哈乐黛</a>致敬，并嵌入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/van-morrison">范·莫里森</a>的《进入神秘》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thin-lizzy">瘦莉兹</a>的《月光下的舞蹈》的片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="U2 - 街道没有名字的地方 - 9-29-2023 - 球体 - 拉斯维加斯" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/plUExiHvmPA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="比真实的更好 - U2 @ The Sphere，拉斯维加斯 2023 年 9 月 29 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4n6owjjvOqk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在对开幕演出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/u2-las-vegas-sphere-setlist-photos-3506848">五星级评价</a>中， <em>NME</em>称赞 U2 在整个演出中使用了“令人惊叹的视觉效果”。</p><p> “达到电影的高潮时，感觉乐队、场地和观众都被带到了莫哈韦沙漠的广阔深处，”它写道。</p><p> “Edge 之前指出，U2 正在将现场音乐会体验‘提升到一个新的水平’，而这个开幕之夜在做到这一点的同时也确保了他们的音乐保持在最前沿。”</p><p>在 U2 的其他新闻中，乐队最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-announce-zoo-station-immersive-fan-experience-ahead-of-sphere-shows-3491076">推出了“Zoo Station”——为粉丝在即将举行的演出之前设计的沉浸式体验</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-pay-tribute-to-absent-drummer-larry-mullen-jr-at-opening-of-las-vegas-sphere-residency-footage-3507759">U2 乐队在 Las Vegas Sphere 驻场演出开幕式上向缺席的鼓手 Larry Mullen Jr 致敬，这首歌曲</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
彼得·凯 (Peter Kay) 认为自己因与利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 不和而被禁止参加全英音乐奖https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peter-kay-thinks-hes-banned-from-brit-awards-due-to-liam-gallagher-feud-3507722?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=peter-凯认为他因利亚姆·加拉格尔不和而被禁止参加全英音乐奖Sam WarnerMon, 02 Oct 2023 11:17:23 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsBrits https://www.nme.com/?p=3507722 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="彼得·凯和利亚姆·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位喜剧演员在 2010 年的颁奖典礼上称加拉格尔为“笨蛋”</p><p>彼得<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peter-kay-thinks-hes-banned-from-brit-awards-due-to-liam-gallagher-feud-3507722">·凯 (Peter Kay) 认为自己因利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 不和而被禁止参加全英音乐奖 (BRIT Awards) 颁奖典礼的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="彼得·凯和利亚姆·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-and-Liam-Gallagher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-kay">彼得·凯</a>表示，由于与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>不和，他已被禁止出席<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英音乐奖</a>颁奖典礼。</p><p> 2010 年，这位喜剧演员在主持当年的颁奖典礼时称这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>乐队主唱为“笨蛋”，因此登上了头条新闻。</p><p>当加拉格尔将麦克风扔向人群时，他正在领取英国 30 年最佳专辑奖，该奖项颁给了 Oasis 的《(What&#39;s the Story) Morning Glory?》。凯然后对观众说：“真是个笨蛋。” </p><figure id="attachment_3507760" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3507760" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3507760" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-live.jpg" alt="彼得·凯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Peter-Kay-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3507760" class="wp-caption-text">喜剧演员彼得·凯 (Peter Kay) 作为特别惊喜嘉宾出现，介绍基恩于 2012 年 5 月 30 日在英国曼彻斯特举行的曼彻斯特阿波罗表演。图片来源：Getty/Shirlaine Forrest/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>凯在他的新传记<em>《电视：小屏幕上的大冒险》</em>中反思了这一事件，并写道（通过<a href="https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/peter-kay-reveals-hes-banned-31061541" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《镜报》</em></a> ）：“利亚姆·加拉格尔获得了奖项。他大摇大摆地走上台去捡起它，然后把它扔到观众席上，然后走开。</p><p> “他可能会用它打到某人的脸。我想，真是个笨蛋。所以当我走回麦克风时我就说了一句‘真是个笨蛋。’”</p><p>这位喜剧演员承认，他“并不是想引起争议，或者制造麻烦”，并补充道：“我只是说出了我的想法。这可能就是为什么我再也没有被邀请回来展示英国人的原因。”</p><p>争议发生后，加拉格尔在推特上提到了凯：“听着，作为一个真正的北方人，我是在两个人的脸上说狗屎，而不是在背后说狗屎的。 LG万岁。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-195-1303285">这位喜剧演员当时在自己的网站上发表了一篇帖子</a>，写道：“昨晚（2 月 16 日）是英国人，我很荣幸被邀请主持这个节目，尤其是它已经有 30 年历史了。</p><p> “恭喜所有获奖者，包括诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)，遗憾的是他没有被提及（庆幸的是他不是一个笨蛋）。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">听着，胖子他妈的，作为一个真正的北方人，我从小就被两个人当着面而不是背后说狗屎。 LG永远活着</p><p>— 利亚姆·加拉格尔 (@liamgallagher) <a href="https://twitter.com/liamgallagher/status/9237577581?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2010 年 2 月 17 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在其他新闻中，凯在他的新书中透露，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peter-kay-wants-to-revive-phoenix-nights-film-3503639">希望将<em>《凤凰之夜》</em>带回电影中</a>。</p><p> “直到今天我才想到布莱恩让年轻的肯尼在俱乐部的屋顶上画了一个巨大的字母‘H’，这样他就可以宣传他们有一个直升机停机坪，”凯写道。 “当然，直升机着陆的可能性为零。</p><p> “随着时间的流逝，我变得越来越像布莱恩，但如果<em>《凤凰之夜》</em>再次崛起，那一定是为了一些非常特别的东西，也许是一部电影？也许布莱恩会被三个鬼魂拜访。现在，这不是一个主意吗？”</p><p> Kay<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/how-to-get-tickets-for-peter-kays-2023-uk-tour-3344918">目前正在英国巡演单口秀<em>《迟到总比不到好》</em></a> ，该节目将持续到 2025 年。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/date-for-brit-awards-2024-revealed-3504879">2024 年全英音乐奖的举办日期最近已确定</a>，颁奖典礼将于 3 月 2 日在 The O2 举行。</p><p>彼得·凯<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peter-kay-thinks-hes-banned-from-brit-awards-due-to-liam-gallagher-feud-3507722">(Peter Kay) 认为自己因利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 不和而被禁止参加全英音乐奖 (BRIT Awards) 颁奖典礼的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Live Aid音乐会将变成舞台音乐剧https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-aid-concert-to-be-turned-into-stage-musical-london-3507736?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=live-aid-concert-to-伦敦音乐剧舞台Charlotte KrolMon, 02 Oct 2023 11:16:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3507736 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鲍勃·格尔多夫" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>鲍勃·格尔多夫 (Bob Geldof) 表示，这个故事是基于 1985 年标志性音乐会当天的真实证词</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-aid-concert-to-be-turned-into-stage-musical-london-3507736">Live Aid 后的音乐会将被改编成舞台音乐剧，</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鲍勃·格尔多夫" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/live-aid-bob-geldof-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《Live Aid》正在被制作成一部音乐剧，将于明年在伦敦上演。</p><p>这部名为<em>《Just For One Day》</em>的音乐剧改编自 1985 年在温布利体育场举行的标志性音乐会，当时包括皇后乐队 (Queen)、U2、大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 和保罗·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 在内的众多艺人都在这场音乐会上表演。</p><p> 1965 年 7 月 13 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-boomtown-rats">，The Boomtown Rats</a>前成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-geldof">Bob Geldof</a>和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ultravox">Ultravox</a>联合主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/midge-ure">Midge Ure</a>组织了这场音乐会，为埃塞俄比亚的饥荒救济筹集资金。</p><p>现在，盖尔多夫已授权剧作家根据音乐会上演一部音乐剧，其中将收录艾尔顿·约翰、奎因和斯汀当天演奏的歌曲。该音乐剧将于2024年1月26日至2024年3月30日在伦敦老维克剧院上演。</p><p><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-66948358" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC 新闻</em></a>采访了格尔多夫，谈论了粉丝们对这部剧的期待。他首先澄清，任何演员都不会试图模仿表演者。</p><p> “这不是致敬的事情。我不会与此有任何关系，”他说。 “所以，没有一个人打扮成弗雷迪，留着蹩脚的小胡子。这些歌曲推动着剧情的发展。”</p><p> The plot of <em>Just For One Day</em> , named after a line in Bowie&#39;s song &#39;Heroes&#39;, will balance a behind-the-scenes look at how Band Aid and Live Aid came together, with a love story inspired by real events.</p><p> “The story is based on actual testimony from the day,” Geldof continued. “It&#39;s real people telling their story throughout this. So it&#39;s complex theatre.” </p><figure id="attachment_3507768" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3507768" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3507768" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/queen-freddie-mercury-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="Freddie Mercury of Queen" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/queen-freddie-mercury-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/queen-freddie-mercury-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/queen-freddie-mercury-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/queen-freddie-mercury-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/queen-freddie-mercury-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/queen-freddie-mercury-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3507768" class="wp-caption-text"> Freddie Mercury of Queen performs with his band at Live Aid, 1985. CREDIT: Jacques Langevin/Sygma/Sygma via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <em>Just For One Day</em> has been green-lit with the full permission of the Band Aid Charitable Trust, which will receive 10 per cent of every ticket sale.</p><p> John O&#39;Farrell, who wrote the <em>Mrs Doubtfire</em> musical, originally conceived the play with the <em>&amp; Juliet</em> musical director Luke Sheppard.</p><p> Craige Els ( <em>Ripper Street</em> , <em>Dr Who</em> ) has been cast as Geldof in the musical. “Let me be completely blunt. It&#39;s bad enough being Bob Geldof. It&#39;s slightly worse seeing someone else pretending to be you,” Geldof told the BBC. “The one upside for me is that he&#39;s got an amazing voice, stage Bob, so that people will think I actually sing as good as that.”</p><p> “And he got the language right,” he continued with a laugh, acknowledging the swearing that he became famous for during the Live Aid broadcast.</p><p> Live Aid was attended by about 72,000 people at London&#39;s Wembley stadium, and, simultaneously more than 89,000 people at the John F. Kennedy Stadium in Philadelphia, US. An estimated 1.9billion people from across 130 countries watched the TV broadcast.</p><p> A 20th anniversary event called Live 8 was held in 2005 at venues in G8 countries and South Africa.</p><p> Meanwhile, last year <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tears-for-fears-open-up-about-missing-live-aid-we-were-exhausted-3139732">Tears For Fears opened up about missing Live Aid in 1985</a> .</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/tears-for-fears-drake-kanye-west-the-tipping-point-3132719">Speaking to <em>NME</em></a> , the duo&#39;s Curt Smith said the group were initially upset with Geldof because he announced that they were performing without their knowledge.</p><p> Additionally, Smith went on to explain that the group were in the middle of a year long tour, with the Live Aid event falling on their only weekend off.</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad0 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><p> Smith said: “Initially, I was pissed off because Bob had announced we were doing it without even asking us and it was smack in the middle of a year-long tour. It was the first week off we had.</p><p> “We kissed and made up with Bob and did <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3hMzR89zB18" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#39;Everybody Wants To Run The World&#39;</a> for him [for Sport Aid] afterwards, but we didn&#39;t think us not performing would affect the amount of money they were raising in any way, so we didn&#39;t do it so we could have that break.”</p></div><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-aid-concert-to-be-turned-into-stage-musical-london-3507736">Live Aid concert to be turned into stage musical</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
